data.description: You'll fall in love with this 2004 brick and vinyl Ranch home in the Ontario school district! The front door welcomes you into the dining room and living room and has great flow to the spacious eat-in kitchen with island, granite countertops, and new appliances, plus a bright sun room with doors to the beautiful rear deck with deck lighting! There are 3 large main floor bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a combined laundry room/half bath on the main floor. The finished basement holds its own charm with a rec room, bonus room (currently used as a billiards room), 4th bedroom, and another half bath! The rear yard is partially fenced – perfect for pets and kids – and has a shed for yard equipment, 2.5-car attached 28'x22' garage, and nice landscaping. The home has also been wired for a whole house portable generator, plus there's a new sump pump and water heater! If you want to see this beautiful home, schedule your showing today!
